\section lua_api_explosion_overview Overview

Explosions are automatically created by \ref lua_api_bomb "bombs"
that explode, and by dying \ref lua_api_enemy "enemies" whose
\ref lua_api_enemy_get_hurt_style "hurting style" is \c "boss".

Explosions hurt the \ref lua_api_hero "hero"
and \ref lua_api_enemy "enemies" that are sensible to them.
But they may also blast \ref lua_api_door "doors"
and can be detected by \ref lua_api_sensor "sensors".

\section lua_api_explosion_inherited_methods Methods inherited from map entity

